             was indicted for <rs id="t17840114-47-off254" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840114-47-off254" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840114-47-off254" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840114-47-victim494" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Drain
                        <interp inst="t17840114-47-victim494" type="surname" value="Drain"></interp>
